data.description: Wow! Perfect for those who love to entertain or relax by fireplace. Open layout of the main floor creates a seamless flow, plenty of space to stretch out. A fenced-in yard, detached garage, and an extra storage shed for even more convenience. Carl Frye Park and Prairie Lincoln Elementary are in close proximity. Located near highway 270 makes commuting a breeze, while nearby shopping and entertainment options ensure you'll never be far from the action.
